      <title>受中国经济衰退影响，保诚股价有望反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/prudential-s-china-fueled-slump-leaves-stock-ripe-for-a-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心该公司在中国的业务风险，今年迄今为止，英国保诚集团 (Prudential Plc) 的股价一直在下跌，以致根据分析师的平均目标价计算，该股目前是富时 100 指数中隐含上涨空间最大的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/prudential-s-china-fueled-slump-leaves-stock-ripe-for-a-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
